        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Guru" href="/users/KacesofCaitsith">KacesofCaitsith</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Guru">Guru</div></div><div class="msgAvatar"></div><div class="msgStar"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/></div><div class="msgWhoNum">278 posts</div>
